data.message: The results are so clean that I thought it was a joke :O

It will be a joke when someone turns this into a product on kickstarter. What I would love to see is an accessible interactive whiteboard, most of what's in the market is cluttered with so much.
Just a damn simple whiteboard, that so happens to digitize everything on it.
Hady Ahmed we can do it as a kick starter :)
مُحَمَّد أبو آدم I'm down for it.
